{"tid":683344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"已設46「天眼」監視垃圾黑點　食環將加推至全港80處","createTime":"2018-05-29T15:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T16:18:33.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b9b20c5904a584b8efef1717108b2e47def4cbe0","tid":683344,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T15:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180529/s00001/bbb07c639c7e9045e22b034107a8fec0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180529%2Fs00001%2Fbbb07c639c7e9045e22b034107a8fec0.jpg&h=d82092d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有傳媒關注，食環署在全港多處加裝網絡攝錄機，並會在下月起全日24小時運作，以助打擊市民亂拋垃圾。食環署最新公布，全港已有46個「垃圾黑點」安裝網絡攝錄機（見圖2、3），其後將逐步擴展至大約80個地點，一年後再檢討成效。署方重申，相關影片只供執法之用，會在半年後銷毀，不會侵犯市民私隱。<br />\n<br />\n《明報》去年11月曾報道，食環署早在2016年12月底展開網絡攝錄機試驗計劃，在6個地點安裝網絡攝錄機，半年後檢討成效，認為有效遏止違例棄置垃圾。諮詢各區議會後，署方決定今年第二季起擴展至各區。<br />\n<br />\n在最新一份新聞稿中，食環署確認已在46個地點安裝網絡攝錄機，下星期三（6月6日）開始運作，之後會逐步擴展至約80個地點。文中又稱，職員將因應實際情況適當調整計劃，包括調整安裝地點，以加強執法成效。日後市民欲查詢各個攝影機位置，可到食環署網頁查看。<br />\n<br />\n食環署強調，實施網絡攝錄機計劃時，依照個人資料私隱專員公署《閉路電視監察及使用航拍機指引》，包括在攝錄範圍內張貼告示；此外亦已制定清晰工作指引，要求員工嚴格遵守收集個人資料的規定。所有錄像披露，僅限於執法需要，如違例事項在6個月內未作檢控，會刪除所涉錄像片段。"},{"pid":"41f654ee77a3558b5bfba43e89b0a10e18ea3e6a","tid":683344,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T15:22:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180529/s00001/bbba9d4801c7ea7aef240db0034faf99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180529%2Fs00001%2Fbbba9d4801c7ea7aef240db0034faf99.jpg&h=f382293b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180529/s00001/bbc04a19aec106aa39d90669a3898c61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180529%2Fs00001%2Fbbc04a19aec106aa39d90669a3898c61.jpg&h=7bb8342d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8bfd8e222907ae91cce0eab32c3c932ee0b87dee","tid":683344,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T15:22:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180529/s00001/1527605394864\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180529%2Fs00001%2F1527605394864&d=xKFZhaTraAzHZhA3f9HzVZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=d8eb8674\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180529%2Fs00001%2F1527605394864&h=d81d850f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180529/s00001/1527605394864</a>"},{"pid":"113a083861f96131554101bc437c57d42d2addd5","tid":683344,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T15:41:36.000Z","msg":"Big brother is"},{"pid":"65e96aa8317ffc102246362d8eb4f4416a745702","tid":683344,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T16:15:15.000Z","msg":"我掉野落地 再執返會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b948bbaf119c87246250af54b3d70409daee59","tid":683344,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65e96aa8317ffc102246362d8eb4f4416a745702","tid":683344,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T16:15:15.000Z","msg":"我掉野落地 再執返會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T16:18:33.000Z","msg":"掉野落地比雀仔食晒都唔計"}]}